  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7 \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0dad \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dc5 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A school girl is arrested for doing an ugly act",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Laggala Police say that they have arrested five people on suspicion of sexually abusing a schoolgirl and a special police team has been deployed to arrest three more suspects.",
        "According to the information given to the police based on the information received by the National Child Insurance Authority, a police team including the Station Commander of Laggala Police, Chief Inspector PBA Ranaweera and the Station Commander of the Children and Women's Bureau, Sub-Inspector Gayani Bandara have started investigations.",
        "Police say that the girl is currently undergoing treatment at the Dambulla Base Hospital.",
        "Police say that the five arrested persons are residents of Laggala Galeya area aged between 19 to 39 and most of them are married.",
        "According to the statements obtained from the girl, information about two other persons was revealed and a police team was dispatched to arrest them, but they fled from the area, the police say.",
        "The police say that it has been reported to the police that this minor girl, who lives in a very poor family in Laggala area, has been brought up under the care of her grandmother.",
        "Local residents say that due to the girl's poverty and lack of social awareness, no one has paid proper attention.",
        "Regarding the incident, Laggala police station chief inspector PB. that. Mr. Ranaweera, Station Commander of Children and Women's Car Bureau, Deputy Police Inspector Gayani Bandara are conducting investigations."
      ],
